The Sith promote competition amongst their ranks, both among the Force Sensitives among their number and their rank and file troops. Those the most merciless, cruel and powerful amongst them are elevated, while those exhibiting softer tendencies are treated like fodder and find death sooner rather than later - often from friendly fire.

These are the former among them. Clad in finer armor and given access to the newest in Imperial weapons technology as reward for their faithful service to the Sith.

This mountain of walking biomass wears some of the heaviest armors created among the Mandalorians.  A lifetime of training, and sheer determination allow this walking fortress to advance, and it will take some heavy ordinance to change their mind.

Trained from a young age, many Mandalorians have an expert eye and good relfexes by the time many are just starting their lives as adults.  Among them though, some Mandalorians truly excel in dealing death from a distance.  Those so gifted are given additional training in the arts of concealment and tracking, and they hunt with a patience that many can only dream of.
